a choisi... vous a choisi...

597
00:37:53,444 --> 00:37:54,106
Clara?

598
00:37:55,107 --> 00:37:57,007
Père, fils...

599
00:37:57,906 --> 00:37:58,516
Oh, mon dieu!

600
00:37:58,616 --> 00:38:00,634
